Package: xyberclan-bootloader
Version: 1.0.0
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: plymouth, plymouth-themes
Recommends: grub-common
Maintainer: psycho237-prog <psychomarlon6@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/CYBERCLAN237/xyberclan-bootloader
Description: Custom boot animation for XYBERCLAN community
 XYBERCLAN Bootloader provides hacker-style boot and shutdown animations
 featuring progressive ASCII art reveal with glitch effects.
 .
 This is an open source community project by XYBERCLAN.
 Features:
  - 9-frame progressive boot animation
  - Glitchy shutdown sequence
  - Plymouth theme integration
  - GRUB customization
  - Cross-distribution support
 .
 Join us at: https://xyber-clan.vercel.app/
